{{other uses|DOD (disambiguation)}} {{italic title}}
'''''Dods Parliamentary Companion''''' (formerly "Dod's Parliamentary Companion") is an annual politics [[reference book]] published in the United Kingdom.<ref>{{ISBN|978-1-908232-25-0}} (2017 edition)</ref>
It provides biographies and contact information on members of the [[Parliament of the United Kingdom|Houses of Parliament]] and the [[Civil Service (United Kingdom)|Civil Service]]. It was first published in 1832 by [[Charles Dod]];<ref>{{cite DNB|wstitle=Dod, Charles Roger Phipps|volume=15}}</ref> and is now published by the firm of [[Dods (publishers)|Dods]].
''Dods'' also publishes on the web as '''Dods People''' (formerly "Dods Online").
